#   udpipe      Tokenisation, lemmatisation, and POS annotation (Section 5)
#
# Optional:
#   hunspell    Dictionary check to drop non-word lemmas (DROP_NONWORDS)
#
# Data Requirements
# -----------------
# - A plain-text (.txt) file of the work to be analysed, named in Section 1.
